        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer103800773" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8551034779210468389">He may have loved Lucy, but I loved Lucy too! I just loved everything about this cute and quirky little romance. The characters were very appealing. Lucy with all her nuances and Theo, my God the man was hot, and loveable. I loved the fact that the author showed both sides, who people think he is versus who he really is. I suppose we all have our preconcieved impressions about personal trainers and it was great to see the author bring this out in the story line.<br/><br/>Loved, loved, loved this book. It </span>
  <span id="freeText8551034779210468389" style="display:none">He may have loved Lucy, but I loved Lucy too! I just loved everything about this cute and quirky little romance. The characters were very appealing. Lucy with all her nuances and Theo, my God the man was hot, and loveable. I loved the fact that the author showed both sides, who people think he is versus who he really is. I suppose we all have our preconcieved impressions about personal trainers and it was great to see the author bring this out in the story line.<br /><br />Loved, loved, loved this book. It kept me entertained from beginning to end. </span>
