        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer219898491" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9033829037790361921">This was a fun read, a mood lifter for sure. When I realized it was a book about weight I almost put it down but am really glad I didn&apos;t. The woman had no pity on herself, she was confident and I really liked that about her. She had a goal and she wanted to succeed, even if her heart was in it way more than she had expected. I flew through this book, it was really, really good!<br/><br/>I will absolutely be reading more from this author. She&apos;s hilarious with a great feel for real human emotion.</span>
  <span id="freeText9033829037790361921" style="display:none">This was a fun read, a mood lifter for sure. When I realized it was a book about weight I almost put it down but am really glad I didn't. The woman had no pity on herself, she was confident and I really liked that about her. She had a goal and she wanted to succeed, even if her heart was in it way more than she had expected. I flew through this book, it was really, really good!<br /><br />I will absolutely be reading more from this author. She's hilarious with a great feel for real human emotion.</span>
